演示视频。这一下大家都知道我在做私活了。</p>\n<p>今天等领导找我谈话吧😭</p>\n", "last_modified": 1724204289, "replies": 115, "id": 1066618}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 222108, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 4227, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 275463, "username": "ryanhui", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ryanhui", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/61c0/4027/275463_mini.png?m=1513677007", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/61c0/4027/275463_normal.png?m=1513677007", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/61c0/4027/275463_large.png?m=1513677007", "created": 1513653418, "last_modified": 1513677007}, "last_reply_by": "momoguo", "last_touched": 1724215515, "title": "女孩子们真的没有压力吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1066593", "created": 1724197858, "deleted": 0, "content": "已经认识的，加上刚认识的，我感觉她们都无忧无虑，一个月挣多少花多少，没事就去吃火锅，开心了就追追演唱会，到处去旅游。经济下行跟她们似乎丝毫没有关系，好羡慕啊，而我只想多攒点钱，我知道总有要花钱的时候。", "content_rendered": "已经认识的，加上刚认识的，我感觉她们都无忧无虑，一个月挣多少花多少，没事就去吃火锅，开心了就追追演唱会，到处去旅游。经济下行跟她们似乎丝毫没有关系，好羡慕啊，而我只想多攒点钱，我知道总有要花钱的时候。", "last_modified": 1724197858, "replies": 102, "id": 1066593}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f854/54e8/422_large.png?m=1605263518", "name": "browsers", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f854/54e8/422_normal.png?m=1605263518", "title": "浏览器", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/browsers", "topics": 723, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Browsers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f854/54e8/422_mini.png?m=1605263518", "stars": 430, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 422, "parent_node_name": "software"}, "member": {"id": 657012, "username": "drymonfidelia", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/drymonfidelia", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/017bcef6e642dbf067e17838a9cd447a?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/017bcef6e642dbf067e17838a9cd447a?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/017bcef6e642dbf067e17838a9cd447a?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1698662217, "last_modified": 1722203860}, "last_reply_by": "lpbname777", "last_touched": 1724212905, "title": "逆天 Chrome，新版本连下载链接都不让看了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1066450", "created": 1724138159, "deleted": 0, "content": "![new-chrome]( https://i.imgur.com/MExdgl3.png)\r\n\r\n点开链接只会打开 https://github.com\r\n\r\n虽然可以从 dev tools 看到实际下载链接，但有的网站下载链接是 js 调用 window.open 打开的，就看不到\r\n\r\n我也很想转 firefox ，但实在太拉跨了，在 bugzilla 反馈过几个 bug ，他们员工也都复现出来了，但是半年多了就是不修，现在只能备用 esr 版 firefox ，正式版 firefox 每天 crash", "content_rendered": "<p><img alt=\"new-chrome\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MExdgl3.png\"/></p>\n<p>点开链接只会打开 <a href=\"https://github.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com</a></p>\n<p>虽然可以从 dev tools 看到实际下载链接，但有的网站下载链接是 js 调用 window.open 打开的，就看不到</p>\n<p>我也很想转 firefox ，但实在太拉跨了，在 bugzilla 反馈过几个 bug ，他们员工也都复现出来了，但是半年多了就是不修，现在只能备用 esr 版 firefox ，正式版 firefox 每天 crash</p>\n", "last_modified": 1724151461, "replies": 100, "id": 1066450}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_large.png?m=1644885960", "name": "car", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_normal.png?m=1644885960", "title": "汽车", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/car", "topics": 2294, "footer": "", "header": "关于买车、开车及汽车文化的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Car", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_mini.png?m=1644885960", "stars": 1929, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 176, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 345913, "username": "zhengdutech", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/zhengdutech", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/78af/b4d7/345913_mini.png?m=1539400694", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/78af/b4d7/345913_normal.png?m=1539400694", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/78af/b4d7/345913_large.png?m=1539400694", "created": 1535679428, "last_modified": 1539400694}, "last_reply_by": "linshuizhaoying", "last_touched": 1724213248, "title": "来群懂哥帮我分析下我目前的情况该买个什么车？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1066410", "created": 1724133039, "deleted": 0, "content": "背景：29 岁，有车有房有老婆有一孩，房贷 2500 一个月(之前提前还贷了)，开了 8 年的马自达昂克赛拉，目前存款现金 50w 多一点点。家庭年收入大概 40 个。\r\n\r\n我一直以来的梦想就是宝马三系，实在是想买，年轻的时候预算不足才上的马 3 ，而且我还想买个二手的，f 地盘 E48 发动机的 320Li 曜夜版的，二手也就 15w 左右，最近看过很多款，就能实现我的梦想。我是真喜欢宝马。\r\n\r\n但是考虑家庭情况，是否需要一次到位换个理想 L6 ？兼顾家庭，主要让老婆孩子坐的舒服，但是说实话冰箱彩电大沙发并不是我的刚需。\r\n\r\n\r\n理想 L6 需要 28w ，二手 3 系 15w 就能到手，我的车还能卖个 3 万多一点。\r\n\r\n兄弟们，我是应该坚持我的宝马梦还是上理想？", "content_rendered": "<p>背景：29 岁，有车有房有老婆有一孩，房贷 2500 一个月(之前提前还贷了)，开了 8 年的马自达昂克赛拉，目前存款现金 50w 多一点点。家庭年收入大概 40 个。</p>\n<p>我一直以来的梦想就是宝马三系，实在是想买，年轻的时候预算不足才上的马 3 ，而且我还想买个二手的，f 地盘 E48 发动机的 320Li 曜夜版的，二手也就 15w 左右，最近看过很多款，就能实现我的梦想。我是真喜欢宝马。</p>\n<p>但是考虑家庭情况，是否需要一次到位换个理想 L6 ？兼顾家庭，主要让老婆孩子坐的舒服，但是说实话冰箱彩电大沙发并不是我的刚需。</p>\n<p>理想 L6 需要 28w ，二手 3 系 15w 就能到手，我的车还能卖个 3 万多一点。</p>\n<p>兄弟们，我是应该坚持我的宝马梦还是上理想？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1724149748, "replies": 94, "id": 1066410}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b53b/3a3d/55_large.png?m=1611920927", "name": "games", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b53b/3a3d/55_normal.png?m=1611920927", "title": "游戏", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/games", "topics": 2776, "footer": "", "header